  "shortDescription": "A quiz extension for GDevelop that fetches trivia questions and checks user answers, perfect for creating trivia games.",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "description": [
    "# TriviaDB Extension for GDevelop",
    "",
    "The **TriviaDB** extension is designed to help you create fun and interactive trivia games in **GDevelop**. It fetches trivia questions and answers, validates user responses, and provides a variety of features to streamline the creation of quiz-based games.",
    "",
    "## Features:",
    "- **Fixed to 4 Questions**: This extension works with a fixed set of 4 trivia questions.",
    "- **Answer Validation**: Automatically validates the selected answer by checking it against the correct answers.",
    "- **Shuffling**: The extension handles the shuffling of answer options, ensuring a fresh experience with every game round.",
    "- **Multiple Difficulty Levels**: Supports fetching trivia questions of varying difficulty levels.",
    "- **Regex Cleaned HTML Tags**: The extension cleans any HTML tags using **RegEx**, ensuring that only plain text is displayed.",
    "- **Reset and Fetch Again**: Allows the scene to be reset, fetching new questions for subsequent rounds.",
    "- **System Info Check**: Press **Shift + I** to check the system information and ensure the extension is running correctly.",
    "",
    "## Requirements:",
    "- **PanelSpriteButton**: Used for displaying interactive buttons that the user can select.",
    "- **ArrayTools**: Essential for managing and manipulating the trivia data in array form.",
    "- **RegEx**: For cleaning and processing the fetched data to remove unwanted HTML tags.",
    "",
    "This extension is a perfect tool for creating trivia games, quiz apps, or interactive knowledge-based experiences within **GDevelop**.",
    "",
